quran[12]{c,v,t}:
  39,10,"Maaku: \"Ko onon yo jeyaa…ìe Am gom…óim…ìe, hulee Joomi mon\". Hino woodani mo∆¥∆¥im…ìe (golle) …ìen e oo aduna, mbarjaari. Leydi Allah ndin ko yaajundi. Anndee mu√±√±ii…ìe …ìen timminirante njo…ìdi ma…ì…ìe ndin, ko aldaa e limoore"
  39,11,"Maaku: \"Min mi yamiraama rewugol Allah, la…ì…ìinana Mo diina kan"
  39,12,"Mi yamiraa kadi, wonugol arano e jebbilii…ìe …ìen"
  39,13,"Maaku : \"Min mi…óo huli, si mi yeddii Joomi am, lepte √ëalaande Mawnde"
  39,14,"Maaku: \"Ko Allah mi rewata, mi la…ì…ìinan Mo diina am"
  39,15,"rewee ko yi…óu…óon onon, hara wanaa Kanko. Maaku: \"Ko woni hayru…ìe …ìen, ko …ìen …ìe tawata √ëalnde Darngal, …ìe hayrinii ko'e ma…ì…ìe, e …ìeynguureeji ma…ì…ìe\". Anndee ko nden woni hayrere …ìanngunde nden"
  39,16,"Hino woodirani …ìe senngo dow ma…ì…ìe, kippoodi Yiite, e kippoodi senngo ley ma…ì…ìe. Ko …óum woni ko Allah hul…ìinirta jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen. Ko onon yo jeyaa…ìe Am, kori hulee Lam"
  39,17,"∆Åen wo…ó…óitor…ìe rewugol bewnooji …ói, …ìe ruttii e Allah, welo-welo no woodani …ìe. Wewlinir jeyaa…ìe Am …ìen"
  39,18,"nanoo…ìe Konngol …ìen, …ìe jokka ko …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥ude e maggol. Ko …ìen woni …ìe Allah fewni …ìen, ko …ìen woni joomiraa…ìe haqqille …ìen"
  39,19,E ko on mo konngol lepte jojji e mun... E ko an da…óndata won…óo ka Yiite
  39,20,"Si ko …ìen hulu…ìe Joomi mun, hino woodani …ìe ku…ìeeje [ka Aljanna] e ku…ìeeje mahaa…óe dow majje, hara can…ói no ila ley majje. Ko fodoore Allah ! Allah non firtataa fodoore. @Corrected"
  39,21,"E a yi'aali, wonnde Allah saa∆¥inirii ndiyam ka kammu, o naadi …óam e nder …ìulli ka leydi; refti O yaltinira …óam remuru seedundu noone, refti ndu …óay…óa, yi'aa hindu soy…ói; refti O wa…óa …óum ko muncaa. Pellet, wonii e …óum, waaju, wonannde joomiraa…ìe haqqille …ìen"